otag \ &amp;\Longrightarrow \ \epsilon_1 (m_e c^2 + \epsilon - \epsilon \cos 	heta) - m_e c^2 \epsilon = 0 
otag \end{align}\] 以上より . \[\epsilon_1 =  rac{\epsilon}{1+  rac{\epsilon}{m_e c^2} (1- \cos 	heta)} 	ag{1}\] この関係を波長に書き換えてみましょう。\(\epsilon = h 
u =  rac{hc}{\lambda}\)より . \[ egin{align} &amp; rac{hc}{\lambda_1} =  rac{ rac{hc}{\lambda}}{1+  rac{1}{m_ec^2}  rac{hc}{\lambda} (1- \cos 	heta)} =  rac{hc}{\lambda}  rac{1}{1+ rac{\lambda_c}{\lambda} (1- \cos 	heta)} =  rac{hc}{\lambda + \lambda_c (1 -\cos 	heta)} 
otag \ &amp;\Longrightarrow \ \lambda_1 - \lambda = \lambda_c (1- \cos 	heta) 	ag{2} \end{align}\]

