abla^2 -  rac{1}{c^2}  rac{\partial^2}{\partial t^2} ight)\int_{-\infty}^\infty d\omega \iiint_{-\infty}^\infty d^3 \mathbf{k} {\hat G}(\mathbf{k}, \omega) e^{-i\omega t+ i\mathbf{k}\cdot \mathbf{r}} 
